Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:58.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,熱氣騰騰的味噌湯和便當搭配也非常合適
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:01.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃 會長簡直是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:03.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 別這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊 四宮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:07.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你不懂冷飯的美味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:07.61,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是跟別人學的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:11.10,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,而是憑藉經驗的發現和靈感創造出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:14.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:16.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜同學一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:18.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可以一起過夜真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:22.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不疼 但是還是想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了藤原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:28.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,絕交吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:32.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輕蔑的程度上升了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 你這樣出招的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:39.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要考慮反擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:42.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,期待明天的到來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:50.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的便當真是費盡心血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:54.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,廚師們好像都來了興致
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:21:01.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 那就快來求我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:02.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,快說讓我分你一口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:06.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣我就以寬大的胸懷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:08.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,給我 給我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:12.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法 那就和會長的便當交換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:13.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣 接受乞求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:16.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 隨時歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:19.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們也吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:20.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:25.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 今天也有好多香腸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:27.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,已經成為固定菜單了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:31.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,很好啊 又可愛又好吃 真是最棒配菜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:33.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,說最棒是不是有點過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:37.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼不好嘛 我就是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:40.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:41.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:44.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得你喜歡吃牡蠣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:48.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,從昨天開始延續到現在的這種不安的氣場到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:52.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼沒來由的給我送高級食材
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:54.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一定在盤算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:21:55.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不然怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:59.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可愛的便當啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.22,0:22:03.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就給可憐的會長一點施捨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:05.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在可憐我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:07.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,太屈辱了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:10.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不能收下 我絕對不能收下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:13.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你給我那麼高級的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:14.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒什麼可回禮的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:16.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,章魚香腸就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:17.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.43,0:22:19.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,疼不疼 腦袋沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:22.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了 怎麼聽起來都像是壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:26.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:30.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嗎 會長也幫忙做了我的份
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.44,0:22:33.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,做一人份還是兩人份都沒什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:36.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:38.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.06,0:22:42.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,便當的配色也很重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.39,0:22:42.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:44.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,人形家畜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:47.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無尊嚴只擅長依靠他人的寄生蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:49.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,營養都去胸上的無腦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.13,0:22:51.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這是何等厚臉皮的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:54.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對不會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:57.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮的眼神像是暗殺者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.57,0:23:00.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 今天社團聯盟要集合
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:01.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要趕快吃完飯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.99,0:23:05.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我的章魚香腸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:07.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.04,0:23:14.32,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.53,0:23:16.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,像個傻子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.78,0:23:20.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:23.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,張開嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.93,0:23:30.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:31.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.61,0:23:44.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同學對不起 我誤會你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:46.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你毫無疑問是個人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:48.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前覺得我是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.60,0:23:50.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出自信來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.13,0:23:54.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都充滿自信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:52.30,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,今日戰局
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.12,0:23:56.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.64,0:24:03.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.53,0:24:06.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長真讓人頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.32,0:24:11.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我午餐都準備成了那樣還是不來告白
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.33,0:24:13.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:17.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,假設輝夜大小姐找到了真正的愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.04,0:24:20.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也會像現在一樣等待被告白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.75,0:24:22.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還是自己主動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.73,0:24:24.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛頭腦戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:28.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這是堵上雙方尊嚴的靈魂的決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.69,0:24:30.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真到了這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.26,0:24:32.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,考慮到別人搶走的風險
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.49,0:24:34.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,合理的結論只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.94,0:24:36.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是主動告白
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.67,0:24:38.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.20,0:24:40.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.70,0:24:42.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是決定…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.70,0:24:43.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.95,0:24:46.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不是因為告白太丟臉了做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.88,0:24:50.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被拒絕了該怎麼辦之類的無聊的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.36,0:24:51.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,才不告白的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.60,0:24:52.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,希望諸位理解
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.77,0:24:58.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事怎麼樣都行吧 這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.70,0:25:12.90,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君と私　きっと今同じ気持ちだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.70,0:25:12.90,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}你和我 現在一定懷著同樣的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.64,0:25:29.97,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君から笑いかけてくれたなら　天使でいられるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.64,0:25:29.97,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}只要有你的微笑 我就還能如天使一般
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.49,0:25:35.99,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}気付いたの　試されてる　意地悪な駆け引きで
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.49,0:25:35.99,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}已經注意到我在用壞心眼的謀略考驗他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.26,0:25:39.05,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}後にはもう引けないから
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.26,0:25:39.05,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}已經不能退縮了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.08,0:25:41.88,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}仕掛けてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.08,0:25:41.88,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}讓我給你設下圈套吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.94,0:25:49.06,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}さあ　掛かってみせて　戸惑ってみせて
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.94,0:25:49.06,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}來吧 掉進陷阱吧 不知所措吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.16,0:25:59.12,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}そして最後に伝えてみせて　好きだって
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.16,0:25:59.12,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}然後在最後說出那句喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.22,0:26:06.82,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君と私　どんな風に恋するの？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.22,0:26:06.81,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}你和我 將會怎樣相戀呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.85,0:26:10.71,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}探る RELATION
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.85,0:26:10.71,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}去探索 RELATION
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.76,0:26:18.32,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}余裕なんてないよ　見つめられる度
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.76,0:26:18.32,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}每次被你注視 我一點都不從容哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.44,0:26:22.13,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}いつも震えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.44,0:26:22.13,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}我總是會顫抖著
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.24,0:26:29.11,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}素直じゃない私を連れ出して！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.24,0:26:29.11,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}請帶走這樣不坦率的我！
